    <item>
      <title>Chromebook 的悔恨：学校对科技的强烈反对不仅仅局限于手机</title>
      <link>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/03/29/technology/chromebook-remorse-kansas-school-laptops.html</link>
      <description><![CDATA[学校笔记本电脑上不再有 YouTube 或视频游戏。课本和铅笔又回来了。一些七年级学生表示，他们更喜欢离线学习。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/03/29/technology/chromebook-remorse-kansas-school-laptops.html</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 29 Mar 2026 16:04:03 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
